               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18440916-name-748" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18440916-name-748" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18440916-name-748" type="surname" value="DASH"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18440916-name-748" type="given" value="WILLIAM HENRY"></interp>WILLIAM HENRY DASH</persName>
                  </hi>. I am in the employ of Martha Dash, my mother—s e is a widow, and keeps a hatter's shop in Tottenham-court-road—she lost a hat on the 10th of Aug.—this is it—I am able to swear it is our make—I am sure it had not been sold—the prisoner has never accounted for sell<lb></lb>ing it—we could not miss it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> The money it was sold for I gave to Mrs. Dash.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18440916-name-749" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18440916-name-749" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
